---
layout: layout.njk
title: Potloodgum A design studio with one employee* that tries to fix the world in tiny steps keeping it human and weird.
description: Potloodgum is a design studio run by Tjerk Dijkstra. Teaching, websites, photography, print and more.
---

<div class="pg-home">

  <div class="pg-home-hero">
    <div class="pg-wordmark">POTLOODGUM</div>
    <p class="pg-home-hero-tagline">A design studio with one&nbsp;employee* that tries to fix the world in tiny steps keeping&nbsp;it human and&nbsp;weird.</p>
    <p class="pg-home-hero-footnote">* that&rsquo;s Tjerk, based in Leeuwarden</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pg-home-grid">

    {% set latestPost = collections.posts | reverse | first %}
    <a href="{{ latestPost.url }}" class="pg-home-card pg-home-card--writing">
      <div class="pg-home-card-label">
        <div class="shape-diamond"></div>
        <span style="color:#e05386">Writing</span>
      </div>
      <div class="pg-home-card-content">
        <div class="pg-home-card-eyebrow">Latest story</div>
        <div class="pg-home-card-title">{{ latestPost.data.title }}</div>
        {% if latestPost.data.description %}<div class="pg-home-card-desc">{{ latestPost.data.description }}</div>{% endif %}
      </div>
      <div class="pg-home-card-more" style="color:#e05386">
        Read story
        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M12.175 9L0 9V7L12.175 7L6.575 1.4L8 0L16 8L8 16L6.575 14.6L12.175 9Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/photography/" class="pg-home-card pg-home-card--photography">
      <img src="/images/photos/25.jpg" alt="Pianist on stage, spotlight from above" class="pg-home-card-bg">
      <div class="pg-home-card-inner">
        <div class="pg-home-card-label">
          <div class="shape-circle"></div>
          <span>Photography</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pg-home-card-overlay-footer">
          <div class="pg-home-card-overlay-title">Slow photography</div>
          <div class="pg-home-card-more">
            See all photos
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M12.175 9L0 9V7L12.175 7L6.575 1.4L8 0L16 8L8 16L6.575 14.6L12.175 9Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/websites/" class="pg-home-card pg-home-card--websites">
      <img src="/images/tienskip.jpg" alt="Tienskip" class="pg-home-card-bg">
      <div class="pg-home-card-inner">
        <div class="pg-home-card-label">
          <div class="shape-square"></div>
          <span>Websites</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pg-home-card-overlay-footer">
          <div class="pg-home-card-overlay-title">Tienskip</div>
          <div class="pg-home-card-more">
            See all websites
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M12.175 9L0 9V7L12.175 7L6.575 1.4L8 0L16 8L8 16L6.575 14.6L12.175 9Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/offline/" class="pg-home-card pg-home-card--offline">
      <img src="/images/videobooth.jpg" alt="Prutt'l Poal videobooth" class="pg-home-card-bg">
      <div class="pg-home-card-inner">
        <div class="pg-home-card-label">
          <div class="shape-rect"></div>
          <span>Offline</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pg-home-card-overlay-footer">
          <div class="pg-home-card-overlay-title">Stuff you can touch</div>
          <div class="pg-home-card-more">
            See offline work
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M12.175 9L0 9V7L12.175 7L6.575 1.4L8 0L16 8L8 16L6.575 14.6L12.175 9Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>
</div>
